metadata.name: Ethereal Horizon
metadata.description: ''Ethereal Horizon" is a captivating abstract landscape painting that captures the dreamlike beauty of a natural setting. The painting's soft colors and fluid brushstrokes evoke a sense of movement and tranquility, while the horizon line serves as a reminder of the vastness and mystery of the natural world. The painting invites the viewer to get lost in a dreamlike, otherworldly landscape.
